To compile Vim 5.7 for use with ParaDySE:
	(1) ./configure --disable-gui --disable-gpm --without-x
	(2) cd src
	(3) make 

To run ParaDySE:
	(1) cd src
	(2) screen (* if you don't install screen, install as follows: sudo apt-get install screen *)
	(3) ../../../bin/run_crest './vim -m -n -Z -i NONE -u NONE' vim.input log 4000 -param vim.w

To clean
	(1) cd src
	(2) make clean

